General.Name: AMP Ltd
General.Description: AMP Limited provides banking, super, and retirement services in Australia and New Zealand. It operates through AMP Bank, Platform, Superannuation & Investments, AMP Bank, and New Zealand Wealth Management (NZWM) segments. The company provides superannuation, retirement, and investment solutions; pension solutions; and SignatureSuper, a retail master trust. It also offers residential mortgages, business financing, deposits and transactional banking services; and wealth management solutions, such as KiwiSaver, corporate superannuation, retail investments, and general insurance. AMP Limited was founded in 1849 and is headquartered in Sydney, Australia.
